{"id":11263,"date":"2013-01-09T13:45:29","date_gmt":"2013-01-09T18:45:29","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=11263"},"modified":"2023-02-06T12:01:48","modified_gmt":"2023-02-06T08:01:48","slug":"vision-allah-full-moon-paradise","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/09\/vision-allah-full-moon-paradise\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Jannah: You will see your Lord like the full moon"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Jarir ibn Abdullah reported: We were with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he looked at the full moon one night. The Prophet said, &#8220;<strong>Verily, you will see your Lord just as you see this moon. There will be no crowd to block your sight. Thus, if you can avoid missing prayer before the rising of the sun and its setting, then do so<\/strong>.&#8221; Then, the Prophet recited the verse, &#8220;<strong>Glorify your Lord with praises before the rising of the sun and its setting<\/strong>.&#8221; (50:39)<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 554, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 633<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/strong><\/em> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0638\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0631\u0650 \u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0629